## Description {#details}

Assign ascending index for instructions in machine basic block.

The index can be used to determine dominance between instructions in same MBB.

Definition at line 68 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/regallocfast-cpp">RegAllocFast.cpp</a>.
